    <PrimAttribute name="minuteOffset" id="13f4c9a7-5bec-414f-9757-93bebfb0a85d">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <text>minuteOffset is the time from the checkpoint to the basetime
(and is relative to the direction of travel). 
For example: For an ARRIVAL, with the basetime at the WHARF,
the 'minuteOffset' will be -10mins (ie. Time at Tanea is 
10mins earlier than the time at the wharf for an arrival).</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
